{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>&quot;Last Shift&quot; is a first person psychological horror videogame with a complete linear story</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>and an average time of completion of 30-40 minutes.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Story</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In it we take on the role of Mark Thompson, who, due to certain issues, loses his job and has to accept a night cleaning job at an office. A relatively simple task, until Mark begins to experience strange occurrences in the office that lead to his disappearance. Months later, a detective delves into this case to uncover what secrets that place hides.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Gameplay</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is primarily a first-person walking simulator with elements of exploration and interaction with different objects in various situations.\u00a1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323670/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1733596714\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Note: This game does not include a save system. It\u2019s designed to be completed in a single session</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Game Features</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unsettling and immersive atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover who is behind Mark's disappearance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore different locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different tasks to complete in each location</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve the mistery if you can</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3323670/7b142c81d2057e6662